title: Elephant Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, International, Beer/Wine, Delivery, Take-out
description: A vegetarian restaurant with clearly marked vegan options. Is part of the Taman Indrakila Hotel. Opened 2013.  Eco and ethical-friendly. Part of the slow food movement. View overlooks the rice terraces in rural Ubud, about 2 kilometers northwest of the Ubud Palace.
